{"tid":1530838,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[置頂］關於連登英文版面守則","createTime":"2019-09-02T05:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T13:23:52.000Z","uid":135762,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"df7d50c2e2b748296b855b7ad36e4cfc29e43d60","tid":1530838,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:18:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家強烈要求連仔開個英文版面/英文台佢哋睇<br />\n<br />\n即係［你問我答］嘅形式<br />\n<br />\n申請連登帳號個申請介面可以轉做英文<br />\n方便佢哋申請帳號<br />\n<br />\n英文台守則希望如下<br />\n<br />\n1.鬼佬諗嘢好直接，唔好post假膠/反串嘅文章<br />\n<br />\n2.另外佢哋唔會mon post <br />\n所有英文台唔好太多廢話 集中着主要資訊<br />\n<br />\n3.唔好有太多冇資訊性嘅留言 ：free hk ,thx,well com.呢一點好重要 太多冇用留言英文用家唔會想睇<br />\n<br />\n4.如果有人洗英文台版  要求admin直接ban<br />\n<br />\n5.可能佢哋唔會主動開post 我哋可以自問自答  就算佢哋唔開post 做CDROM一樣有嘢睇<br />\n<br />\n有啲咩規則各位可以再定<br />\n再加以討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中國有一國兩制<br />\n連登都要有一討兩規矩</span></span>"},{"pid":"c059b908212d57b464f699865a081e0f40f01357","tid":1530838,"uid":290207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:21:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"596d3efc3b5010f4c0c457b0364bb5a7136d5593","tid":1530838,"uid":133743,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:39:27.000Z","msg":"Push. Don&rsquo;t play too much plastic, not easy for foreigners to understand plastic"},{"pid":"bd7e38c736186fa289eaf2c896d7f8fb9262e7eb","tid":1530838,"uid":205482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit)<br />\n5. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n6. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣<br />\n7. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n8. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n9. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n10. 不要說推，試著將呢整個訊息copy and paste嚟推post#kill<br />\n11. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。<br />\n<br />\n利申：我做緊。你呢？"},{"pid":"048a487de754973ea36d6dd2fa2120d48af006f5","tid":1530838,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:40:47.000Z","msg":"其實連仔可唔可以整到個即時翻譯功能出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f287f6df7b479d40eb14b1a810908120fdff6423","tid":1530838,"uid":257422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZykHbrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZykHbrV.jpg&h=30a62641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Make Hong Kong great again! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民發夢合唱</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國歌</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <span style=\"color: gold;\">We should learn how to sing</span><br />\n <em><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;The Star-</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">Spangled Banner&quot;</span></em><br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家仲記唔記得手足揮美國國旗唱美國國歌唱到Trump Trump都retweet!!!!</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets